      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Regulations)</block>
            <p>These Regulations are made in exercise of the powers conferred by paragraph 1(1) and (3) of schedule 2 of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act <ref eId="c00013" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukpga/2018/16">2018 (c. 16)</ref> to address failures of retained EU law to operate effectively, and other deficiencies, arising from the withdrawal of the United Kingdom from the European Union.</p>
            <p>These Regulations make amendments to subordinate legislation in the field of food nutrition in relation to Scotland.</p>
            <p>An impact assessment has not been produced for this instrument as no significant impact on the private or voluntary sector is foreseen.</p>
         </blockContainer>
      </conclusions>
